    "[37] Figure 8 shows two clusters, red and blue.",
    "Red is the most significant cluster consisting of 14 keywords which are outlier detection, fraud, smote, ANN, RF, SVM, decision tree, LR, KNN, naïve Bayes, supervised machine learning, random forest, and k nearest neighbor.",
    "Blue cluster comprises 4 keywords which are ensemble, accuracy, precision, and recall.",
    "Distribution and nature of collaboration at the country levelThere are 642 documents issued by 63 different nations.",
    "India produced the most publications (198 documents, or 30.6% of the total), followed by China (71 publications, or 10.97% of the total)."
